    public class MergeElementImpl
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.impl.MinimalEObjectImpl.Container
implements MergeElement
    An implementation of the model object 'Merge Element'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Bucket From
    • Bucket To
    • Previous
    • Next
    • Part From In To
    • Part To In From
    • Element Start
    • Element End
    • Seconds
